# Lenses — operator-imported steering

Operator-imported specialist context the four roles apply on demand (see SKILL.md → *Lenses*).
This file is the registry. Empty until the first `/gitos agent import`. Lenses are read-on-demand
*approach* context — not the brain (which holds facts). A machine-local **global library** may also
exist at `<skill>/agents/` — its lenses apply here too (this repo's same-named lens wins); `import`
seeds both layers, and `upgrade` offers to refresh this repo's copies from it. In **Applies to**,
`[any]` = every role.

